General.Name: StoneBridge Acquisition Corporation Warrant
General.Description: StoneBridge Acquisition Corporation intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It intends to focus its search on a target with operations in the consumer technology, communications, software, SaaS, fintech, or media sectors. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
